    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like such a weight on everyone. i was looking at the bills today and then looking at my kids and i just... it doesn't add up. i'm just spending money we don't have and taking up space and energy that could be going to them. it feels like the math of my life is just negative right now.",
